Sys-SyslogMessages version 0.01
===============================

This is a simple module that figures out where the syslog from
the syslog.conf or the syslog-ng.conf and can copy it or tail it.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


